    "name": "破碎怪谈：雾雨村",
    "steam_appid": 3014520,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>《破碎怪谈：雾雨村》</strong>是一款心理恐怖游戏，背景设定于风景如画的日本雾雨村。 这片土地被古老传说所缠绕——源自日本民间传说的巨大骸骨 <i>饿者骷髅</i>正蛰伏于此。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3014520/extras/a4df5415fa2ff51a7fcf65dc74d2d29f.poster.avif?t=1751089070\" width=600 height=252 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3014520/extras/a4df5415fa2ff51a7fcf65dc74d2d29f.webm?t=1751089070\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3014520/extras/a4df5415fa2ff51a7fcf65dc74d2d29f.mp4?t=1751089070\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>游戏目标</strong><br>➤ 揭露深埋于血脉中的憎恨根源<br>➤ 探索雾雨村环形封闭的幽闭路径结构<br>➤ 引入象征悲剧事件永劫循环的「轮回游戏机制」<br> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3014520/extras/7b80c039a7eb2d07ab80bec7f71dcf94.poster.avif?t=1751089070\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3014520/extras/7b80c039a7eb2d07ab80bec7f71dcf94.webm?t=1751089070\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3014520/extras/7b80c039a7eb2d07ab80bec7f71dcf94.mp4?t=1751089070\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>故事背景</strong> <br>直美·蒙哥马利为开启音乐事业来到雾雨村，却意外陷入诡异力量的围困，她在这里逐步揭开村落被诅咒的秘辛。她的穿越之旅将串联记忆碎片，为后续作品<strong>破碎怪谈：恶意取关</strong>中的事件叙述奠定基础。<br><br>随着笼罩村落的黑暗传说逐渐显现，诡谲氛围愈加强烈。传说村子中央曾有一座古老神社（现已消失），但这一场诅咒让所有的居民陷入了悲剧之中。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3014520/extras/b6112d3218e687d5a6ea5b1b64f528e4.poster.avif?t=1751089070\" width=600 height=252 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3014520/extras/b6112d3218e687d5a6ea5b1b64f528e4.webm?t=1751089070\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3014520/extras/b6112d3218e687d5a6ea5b1b64f528e4.mp4?t=1751089070\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong></strong><br><strong>核心特色</strong><br>➤ 实景级画质<br>➤ 游戏中雕像由意大利著名雕塑家<i>布鲁诺·卢基（Bruno Lucchi） </i>创作<br>➤ 特邀心理学专家参与开发，注重对玩家的情感共鸣<br> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3014520/extras/f833b573fcd389d2a8279375e5b32b04.poster.avif?t=1751089070\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3014520/extras/f833b573fcd389d2a8279375e5b32b04.webm?t=1751089070\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3014520/extras/f833b573fcd389d2a8279375e5b32b04.mp4?t=1751089070\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><strong></strong><br> <br>雾雨村被设计为一座自循环的谜之迷宫，象征主角错误决策与破碎命运的轮回。游戏通过环境微妙的变化与重复，驱使玩家在深入故事的同时寻找打破宿命闭环的契机。嫉妒、野心等人性议题将贯穿游戏。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3014520/extras/a527dc277e8a6cde8839a5fe809d9c63.poster.avif?t=1751089070\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3014520/extras/a527dc277e8a6cde8839a5fe809d9c63.webm?t=1751089070\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3014520/extras/a527dc277e8a6cde8839a5fe809d9c63.mp4?t=1751089070\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >可以在平台上关注 <strong>破碎怪谈</strong> 系列！</p>",
    "supported_languages": "英语<strong>*</strong>, 法语, 意大利语, 德语, 西班牙语 - 西班牙, 日语, 韩语, 波兰语, 葡萄牙语 - 葡萄牙, 俄语, 简体中文, 繁体中文, 土耳其语, 乌克兰语, 葡萄牙语 - 巴西, 西班牙语 - 拉丁美洲<br><strong>*</strong>具有完全音频支持的语言",
